Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: fantasy-agn
Version: 1.0.0
Summary:  FANTASY - Fully Automated pythoN tool for AGN Spectra analYsis, a python based code for simultaneous multi-component fitting of AGN spectra, optimized for the optical rest-frame band (3600-8000A), but also applicable to the UV range (2000-3600A) and NIR range (8000-11000A).
Author: Nemanja
Author-email: rakinemanja@gmail.com
